OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with spells of rain,
OL,6,Flocally heavy, moving erratically
OL,7,Fnortheastwards across northern parts
OL,8,Fduring Thursday morning. Rain easing
OL,9,Finto the afternoon with some sunny
OL,10,Fintervals along the coast and in the
OL,11,Fsouth. Warm and muggy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRain in the north clears
OL,14,Fduring the evening with cloud
OL,15,Flingering in the west, reasonable
OL,16,Fbreaks in the cloud develop in the
OL,17,Feast. Winds light but breezy along the
OL,18,Fcoast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
